## Detection Logic
```go
func isFullyBlocked(ws Workstream) (bool, []Issue) {
    blockers := []Issue{}
    hasActionable := false

    for _, issue := range ws.Issues {
        if issue.Status == "open" || issue.Status == "in_progress" {
            hasActionable = true
            if isBlocked(issue) {
                // Find external blockers (not in this workstream)
                for _, dep := range issue.BlockedBy {
                    if !isInWorkstream(dep, ws) {
                        blockers = append(blockers, dep)
                    }
                }
            } else {
                return false, nil  // Has unblocked actionable item
            }
        }
    }

    return hasActionable && len(blockers) > 0, unique(blockers)
}
```

## Visual Indicators
- âš ï¸ warning emoji in header
- Yellow/orange highlight on blocked workstream
- "BLOCKING THIS WORKSTREAM" section at top of expanded view
- Blockers grouped by their label for clarity

